## Guidelines for Screenshots
- Use consistent device frames
- Show realistic data (use demo account)
- Maintain high resolution (1080p+)
- Use light theme for consistency
- Crop to remove unnecessary UI elements

## Recommended Tools
- Flutter Device Preview for consistent frames
- Browser DevTools for web screenshots
- Figma/Canva for adding device frames
